products.name: Dress Lady Frock
products.detail: Lulus Exclusive! Take a jaunt through the gardens with the Lulus French Countryside Blush Floral Print High-Low Dress! Lovely purple and green floral print woven poly sweeps across a surplice bodice framed by cute cap sleeves. Tying waist sash tops a wrapping, high-low skirt. Hidden back zipper.
